overview: Natural Born Breeders presents Bareback Buffet. Otter Jack Winters is introduced to Jacob Woods in the early morning at Letherwerks. Jack is eager to test drive Jacob's furry hole for his own pleasure. Getting the job done, it appears that Jacob has no complaints and wants to have his hole loaded. Sliding in the sling Jack proves that he can drive into Jacob's hole and breed him as a good Otter should.
title: Bareback Buffet
